OL,3,CDavid Beckham becomes UK's first
OL,4,Cbillionaire sportsperson
OL,6,FSir David Beckham has become the UK's
OL,7,Ffirst billionaire sportsperson, as he
OL,8,Fand his wife Victoria appeared on the
OL,9,F2026 Sunday Times Rich List.
OL,11,FThe collective wealth of the Beckhams
OL,12,Fpassed the billion-pound mark this
OL,13,Fyear, according to the compilers of
OL,14,Fthe list, reaching #1.185bn.
OL,16,FThat placed them second in the Sunday
OL,17,FTimes' list of wealthiest
OL,18,Fsportspeople, behind the family of ex-
OL,19,FFormula One chief executive Bernie
OL,20,FEcclestone, whose wealth was placed at
OL,21,F#2bn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
