FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778861473
OL,3,CDavid Beckham becomes UK's first
OL,4,Cbillionaire sportsperson
OL,6,FFormer England captain Beckham is a co-
OL,7,Fowner of Inter Miami, estimated to be
OL,8,FMajor League Soccer's most valuable
OL,9,Fclub at $1.45bn (#1.07bn).
OL,11,FHe has also made huge sums as a brand
OL,12,Fambassador for companies such as
OL,13,FAdidas and Hugo Boss.
OL,15,FVictoria Beckham's wealth has
OL,16,Fprimarily been generated from the
OL,17,Ffashion label she set up in her name,
OL,18,Fhaving originally found fame and
OL,19,Ffortune as a member of the Spice Girls.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
