FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778861473
OL,3,CDavid Beckham becomes UK's first
OL,4,Cbillionaire sportsperson
OL,6,FThe Beckhams have been in the
OL,7,Fheadlines heavily in recent months
OL,8,Fafter their son, Brooklyn, publicly
OL,9,Fmade clear he no longer wished to have
OL,10,Fthem in his life.
OL,12,FBrooklyn claimed they were unwelcoming
OL,13,Fto his now wife, Nicola Peltz, and
OL,14,Frecounted numerous awkward engagements
OL,15,Fwith his parents, describing them more
OL,16,Fas business operatives rather than
OL,17,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
