PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778861473
OL,3,CDavid Beckham becomes UK's first
OL,4,Cbillionaire sportsperson
OL,6,FWhile the Beckhams saw their wealth
OL,7,Fgrow over the last 12 months, Sir Jim
OL,8,FRatcliffe, the co-owner of Beckham's
OL,9,Fformer club Manchester United, has
OL,10,Fdropped down the overall Rich List
OL,11,Ffrom seventh to ninth.
OL,13,FHis fortune shrank by #1.85bn,
OL,14,Faccording to the list compilers, to
OL,15,F#15.194bn.
OL,17,FThe list compilers lowered the value
OL,18,Fof his petrochemicals company Ineos to
OL,19,F#17bn, owing to "rising debt, falling
OL,20,Frevenues and a loss of #515.7million".
OL,26,@{D@QOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
