OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778861473
OL,3,CDavid Beckham becomes UK's first
OL,4,Cbillionaire sportsperson
OL,6,FThat was less of a drop compared to
OL,7,Fthe year before, when the list
OL,8,Fcompilers said his wealth plummeted by
OL,9,Fover #6bn.
OL,11,FJoining Beckham on the richest
OL,12,Fsportspeople list are promoters Barry
OL,13,Fand Eddie Hearn, whose combined wealth
OL,14,Fwas estimated at #1.035bn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
