PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1778861473
OL,3,CDavid Beckham becomes UK's first
OL,4,Cbillionaire sportsperson
OL,6,FEddie Hearn is the promoter of British
OL,7,Fheavyweight Anthony Joshua, who is
OL,8,Feighth on the list with a fortune of
OL,9,F#240m. That places him above another
OL,10,Fheavyweight, Tyson Fury, who is ninth
OL,11,Fon #162m.
OL,13,FHearn announced last month that Joshua
OL,14,Fhad signed a deal to fight Fury, with
OL,15,Fno confirmed date or venue as yet.
OL,17,FSeven-time F1 champion Sir Lewis
OL,18,FHamilton is fifth on the list (#435m),
OL,19,Fwhile back-to-back Masters golf
OL,20,Fchampion Rory McIlroy is seventh with
OL,21,F#325m.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
